<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ulazno vratilo
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Utisnite lijevi ležaj (2) posebnim alatom i hidrauličnom prešom.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B024">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-80113">
09913-80113
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Istim specijalnim alatom kao u 10. koraku postavite odstojnik zupčanika 5. stupnja (1).
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Da biste spriječili deformiranje odstojnika zupčanika 5. stupnja (1) zbog prevelike kompresije, ne ugrađujte ga pod pritiskom istovremeno s lijevim ležajem (2).
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A520020.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "59.848mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "153"/>
